title: Tusen and 2 Restaurang and Bar
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, International, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Burger restaurant where whole menu can be made vegan by requesting the vegan burger. Set menu includes option of fries, potato wedges, salad or bulgur and a soft drink or mineral water. Sets from 90 SEK (~10 Euros) and up. Special lunch price 69 SEK (~8 Euros). Has outdoor seating. Accepts credit cards. Open Mon-Thur 11-21, Fri 11-22, Sat 12-22, Sun 13-21. Sister restaurant in Malmo.
